    {
      "index": 7,
      "title": "Triceps Pushdown",
      "notes": "Sets: 2 Working Sets.\n\nTarget: 10-15 reps @ RPE 10.\n\nRest: 1m 30s\n\nHardware Pivot: Utilize a fixed straight bar or V-bar. Abandon the rope to eliminate the cognitive overhead of \"tearing\" the handles apart. Focus 100% of CNS output on driving the weight downward.\n\nPostural Guardrail: No shrugging. Shoulders locked down away from ears.\n\nLockout: Pin elbows to ribs. Full lockout at bottom.",
